{"tid":154067,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"M$ 終於收手！Windows 10 唔再逼人更新","createTime":"2017-03-13T04:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T15:45:48.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16729cfe0ec9020f6c71963bb8e6b02dbd457d26","tid":154067,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:36:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">微軟終於放手，Windows 10 強制更新退場！<br />\n<a href=\"http://3c.ltn.com.tw/m/news/29129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2F29129&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=950c86bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2F29129&h=ddb07775\" target=\"_blank\">http://3c.ltn.com.tw/m/news/29129</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2017/03/08/170308-29129-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2017%2F03%2F08%2F170308-29129-1.jpg&h=247b7f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 Windows 10 推出初期，由於提供免費升級，吸引不少用戶選擇更新 Windows 7、Windows 8.1 等老舊作業系統。然而由於更新手段過於強硬、沒有明確取消更新的方式，讓不少用戶抱怨微軟（Microsoft）沒有讓用戶有選擇的機會。<br />\n<br />\n對此《Cnet》報導指出，微軟已經決定取消 Windows 10 強制更新的設計，未來在 Windows 10 Creators Update 更新上，用戶不會再看到無法略過的強制更新選項。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2017/03/08/170308-29129-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2017%2F03%2F08%2F170308-29129-2.png&h=d76970da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該報導出，微軟將提供 Windows 10 用戶選擇的權力，包含「立刻重新啟動」來完成更新、「選定時間」在未來特定時段更新、或是選擇「靜音」來略過系統更新通知。<br />\n<br />\n當中的重點在於，就算用家什麼都不做、關閉該通知回到桌面，Windows 10 系統也不會強制關機。藉此 Windows 10 用戶可以持續第避免系統升級，每一次的「Snooze」選項可以讓升級通知延後 3 天，最多可延展到 365 天。"},{"pid":"dbe75cbbb5f00c9880e38071f69500e28e278337","tid":154067,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:08:42.000Z","msg":"蝗恩浩蕩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72223e8c043cfc8a7fa35ac8cc23f95e6b84687c","tid":154067,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:10:53.000Z","msg":"m$: 等window 11出黎先炸你"},{"pid":"4129d1c6bb84c3c0a7c4e64b359e7377c9d35c1d","tid":154067,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"下? 唔係應該㗎咩? 之前啲版本強制更新㗎?"},{"pid":"58e465132e66e2ee91465016f5a499c4eb344d62","tid":154067,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下? 唔係應該㗎咩? 之前啲版本強制更新㗎?</blockquote><br />\n食開屎既人有日唔洗食屎已經係福氣"},{"pid":"213fb1fe5a67151fdcbdbcb0854064512255a82f","tid":154067,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下? 唔係應該㗎咩? 之前啲版本強制更新㗎?</blockquote><br />\n食開屎既人有日唔洗食屎已經係福氣</blockquote><br />\n點屎法？"},{"pid":"fdfc23f72912ac9d2919d76ef3eee2da20347628","tid":154067,"uid":84783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T11:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>m$: 等window 11出黎先炸你</blockquote><br />\n應該唔會有"},{"pid":"3253db22f8f2f5bde765fd95005bbe5faa663436","tid":154067,"uid":83754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}